== 演化 ==

=== 演化史 ===
依照目前较广泛接受的研究，植物（[[原始色素體生物|原始色素體生物]]）起源于16亿年前的一次[[共生體學說|内共生]]事件<ref name=":3">{{Cite journal|title=How the first plant came to be|url=http://www.nature.com/news/how-the-first-plant-came-to-be-1.10048|last=Biello|first=David|journal=Nature News|doi=10.1038/nature.2012.10048|language=en|access-date=2019-02-10|archive-date=2018-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180419074424/https://www.nature.com/news/how-the-first-plant-came-to-be-1.10048|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中的[[色素體|质体]]、[[線粒體|线粒体]]等结构，则可以追溯到更早存在的[[蓝藻|蓝藻]]和[[好氧細菌|好氧細菌]]<ref name="Lynn" />。

[[蓝藻|蓝藻]]的历史没有定论，最早的可能记录是超过35亿年前的蓝藻黏结堆砌而成的[[疊層石|疊層石]]，但仍有争议<ref name="PiP">{{cite journal|title=Patterns In Palaeontology: The first 3 billion years of evolution|url=http://www.palaeontologyonline.com/articles/2012/patterns-in-palaeontology-the-first-3-billion-years-of-evolution/|last=Garwood|first=Russell J.|journal=Palaeontology Online|accessdate=2015-06-25|issue=11|year=2012|volume=2|pages=1–14|archive-date=2019-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522210148/https://www.palaeontologyonline.com/articles/2012/patterns-in-palaeontology-the-first-3-billion-years-of-evolution/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在最晚16亿年前，植物的最后共同祖先以蓝藻为食，但在食物缺乏且阳光充足的环境下，与蓝藻共生，利用它们进行光合作用比将蓝藻作为食物更有利于生存，因此植物的祖先与蓝藻发生了内共生，并获得了质体和光合作用的能力，而一种类似衣原体的生物（可能是[[軍團菌屬|軍團菌]]，包括引发[[军团病|军团病]]的种类）则提供了将有机物转运出质体的基因<ref name=":3" />。

传统上认为有胚植物是最早的陆生植物，但近年来有研究指出，通过对古土壤的化学和地质学分析可以看出，早在10亿年前就有陆生单细胞藻类<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Earth’s earliest non-marine eukaryotes|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/nature09943|last=Wellman|first=Charles H.|last2=Martin D. Brasier|date=2011-05|journal=Nature|issue=7348|doi=10.1038/nature09943|volume=473|pages=505–509|language=en|issn=1476-4687|last3=Battison|first3=Leila|last4=Strother|first4=Paul K.|access-date=2019-02-11|archive-date=2019-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331230322/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature09943|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[有胚植物|有胚植物]]起源于[[轮藻门|轮藻]]，最早产生于[[奥陶纪|奥陶纪]]中期<ref name="NiklasKutschera2010">{{Citation|last=Niklas|first=K.J.|title=The evolution of the land plant life cycle|year=2010|postscript=.|last2=Kutschera|first2=U.|journal=New Phytologist|volume=185|issue=1|pages=27–41|doi=10.1111/j.1469-8137.2009.03054.x|pmid=19863728}}</ref><ref name="Vries2018">{{cite journal|title=Plant evolution: landmarks on the path to terrestrial life.|first1=J|last2=Archibald|first2=JM|date=March 2018|journal=The New Phytologist|issue=4|doi=10.1111/nph.14975|volume=217|pages=1428–1434|pmid=29318635|last1=de Vries}}</ref>，传统观点认为其起源于海洋藻类，但也有研究指出其起源于陆生单细胞藻类<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Why Plants Were Terrestrial from the Beginning|url=http://www.cell.com/trends/plant-science/abstract/S1360-1385(15)00300-3|last=Harholt|first=Jesper|last2=Moestrup|first2=Øjvind|date=2016-02-01|journal=[[Trends_(journals)|Trends in Plant Science]]|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.tplants.2015.11.010|volume=21|pages=96–101|pmid=26706443|last3=Ulvskov|first3=Peter}}</ref>；[[维管植物|維管植物]]出現於[[志留紀|志留紀]]時，且到了[[泥盆纪|泥盆纪]]時已辐射并分布在許多不同类型的陆地生態系统中<ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|title=The evolution of the land plant life cycle|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1111/j.1469-8137.2009.03054.x|last=Niklas|first=Karl J.|last2=Kutschera|first2=Ulrich|date=2010-01|journal=New Phytologist|issue=1|doi=10.1111/j.1469-8137.2009.03054.x|volume=185|pages=27–41|language=en}}</ref><ref name="Vries20182">{{cite journal|title=Plant evolution: landmarks on the path to terrestrial life.|first1=J|last2=Archibald|first2=JM|date=March 2018|journal=The New Phytologist|issue=4|doi=10.1111/nph.14975|volume=217|pages=1428–1434|pmid=29318635|last1=de Vries}}</ref>；早期[[种子植物|種子植物]]——[[種子蕨|種子蕨]]和[[科達樹|科達樹]]出現於[[泥盆纪|泥盆纪]]晚期並於[[石炭紀|石炭紀]]時開始分歧，之後經過[[二叠纪|二叠纪]]和[[三疊紀|三疊紀]]而有了更多的演化<ref name="Novikov2015">{{cite journal|title=Modern plant systematics|author=Novíkov & Barabaš-Krasni|journal=|publisher=Liga-Pres|issue=|doi=10.13140/RG.2.1.4745.6164|year=2015|volume=|pages=685|isbn=978-966-397-276-3}}</ref><ref name="Anderson2007">{{cite journal|title=Brief history of the gymnosperms: classification, biodiversity, phytogeography and ecology|author=Anderson, Anderson & Cleal|journal=Strelitzia|publisher=SANBI|issue=|doi=|year=2007|volume=20|pages=280|isbn=978-1-919976-39-6}}</ref><ref name="Rothwelletal989">{{cite journal|title=''Elkinsia'' gen. nov., a Late Devonian gymnosperm with cupulate ovules|url=|journal=Botanical Gazette|issue=|doi=10.1086/337763|year=1989|volume=150|pages=170–189|author3=Gillespie W. H.|author1=Rothwell G. W.|author2=Scheckler S. E.}}</ref>；[[被子植物門|被子植物]]是最後出現的植物類群，於[[侏羅紀|侏羅紀]]時由古[[裸子植物|裸子植物]]中演化出來，並於[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]時迅速地分歧出許多物種，并一直繁盛至今，成为陆生植物的最优势类群<ref name="Davies2004">{{cite journal|title=Darwin's abominable mystery: Insights from a supertree of the angiosperms|first1=T. J.|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=7|doi=10.1073/pnas.0308127100|year=2004|volume=101|pages=1904–9|bibcode=2004PNAS..101.1904D|pmc=357025|pmid=14766971|last1=Davies}}</ref>；现代裸子植物（称为[[末端裸子植物|末端裸子植物]]）是与被子植物并列的独立单系分支，并非被子植物的祖先<ref name="pnas">{{Cite journal|title=An uncorrelated relaxed-clock analysis suggests an earlier origin for flowering plants|url=http://www.pnas.org/content/107/13/5897|last=Smith|first=Stephen A.|last2=Beaulieu|first2=Jeremy M.|date=2010-03-30|journal=''Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences''|issue=13|doi=10.1073/pnas.1001225107|volume=107|pages=5897–5902|language=en|issn=0027-8424|pmc=2851901|pmid=20304790|last3=Donoghue|first3=Michael J.|access-date=2019-02-09|archive-date=2018-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181208002807/https://www.pnas.org/content/107/13/5897|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="APweb"><u>[http://www.mobot.org/MOBOT/Research/APweb/orders/Cycadales.html#Gymnosperms Gymnosperms] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mobot.org/MOBOT/Research/APweb/orders/Cycadales.html#Gymnosperms |date=20190207040855 }}</u>. In Stevens, P. F. (2001 onwards). Angiosperm Phylogeny Website. Version 9, June 2008 [and more or less continuously updated since].</ref>。

=== 化石记录 ===
{{Main|古植物学||}}植物的[[化石|化石]]包括[[根|根]]、[[茎|茎]]、[[葉|葉]]、[[種子|種子]]、[[果实|果实]]、[[花粉|花粉]]、[[孢子|孢子]]和[[琥珀|琥珀]]。植物化石在陸地上、湖泊中、河流裡以及近海內的地層都有发现的记录。[[花粉|花粉]]、[[孢子|孢子]]和藻類的化石被用來界定地層岩石的順序。殘留的植物化石並不如動物化石那麼普遍，然而植物化石在世界上許多地區之內，都可以有大量的發現。[[File:Petrified_forest_log_1_md.jpg|250px]]中的[[硅化木|硅化木]]]]最早可以被明确归类于植物的化石是一种学名叫''{{Internal link helper/en|Rafatazmia chitrakootensis|Rafatazmia}}''的红藻，生活在16亿年前，发现于[[印度地理|印度]]的[[疊層石|疊層石]]中<ref name="Rafatazmia"/>。

[[绿色植物|绿色植物]]最早的化石是澳大利亚卢坡群(Roper Group)的一些[[微体化石|微体化石]]，生活在15亿年－13亿年前，其结构与现代绿藻类似<ref>{{cite journal|title=TEM evidence for eukaryotic diversity in mid-Proterozoic oceans|last=Javaux|first=Emmanuelle J.|journal=Geobiology|issue=3|doi=10.1111/j.1472-4677.2004.00027.x|year=2004|volume=2|pages=121–132|author3=Walter, Malcolm R.|author2=Knoll, Andrew H.}}</ref>。

最早的与现生类群有明确亲缘关系的植物化石是''{{Internal link helper/en|Bangiomorpha pubescens|Bangiomorpha}}''，是一种生活在12亿年前的红藻<ref>{{cite journal|title=''Bangiomorpha pubescens'' n. gen., n. sp.: implications for the evolution of sex, multicellularity, and the Mesoproterozoic/Neoproterozoic radiation of eukaryotes|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_paleobiology_summer-2000_26_3/page/386|last=Butterfield|first=Nicholas J.|journal=Paleobiology|issue=3|doi=10.1666/0094-8373(2000)026<0386:BPNGNS>2.0.CO;2|year=2000|volume=26|pages=386–404}}</ref>。

[[轮藻门|轮藻门]]的一些植物的[[細胞壁|细胞壁]]发生[[钙化|钙化]]，因此比其他藻类更容易留下化石记录，可追溯到[[志留紀|志留纪]]晚期（大约4.1亿年前）<ref name="Raven8th" />{{Rp|356}}，例如[[派卡藻|派卡藻]]（''Parka decipiens''），''Palaeonitella cranii'' 等<ref name="Hemsley">{{cite journal|title=The ultrastructure of the spores of the Devonian plant ''Parka decipiens''|last=Hemsley|first=A.R.|journal=Annals of Botany|issue=3|doi=10.1093/oxfordjournals.aob.a087852|year=1989|volume=64|pages=359–367}}</ref><ref name="Kelman2003">{{cite journal|title=Charophyte algae from the Rhynie chert|first1=R.|last2=Feist|first2=M.|journal=Transactions of the Royal Society of Edinburgh: Earth Sciences|issue=4|doi=10.1017/s0263593300000808|year=2003|volume=94|pages=445–455|last3=Trewin|first3=N.H.|last4=Hass|first4=H.|last1=Kelman}}</ref>。

有胚植物已知最古老的[[遗迹化石|遗迹化石]]源于[[奥陶纪|奥陶纪]]，但此類化石是零碎不全的。到了[[志留紀|志留紀]]才有完整的化石被保留下來，包括[[石松門|石松門]]的「[[刺石松|刺石松]]」。[[泥盆紀|泥盆紀]]之後，[[萊尼蕨門|萊尼蕨門]]的詳細化石在此時期被發現，此化石顯示出了其植物組織的單一細胞。泥盆紀時亦出現了被認為是最古老樹木的植物「[[古羊齒屬|古羊齒屬]]」，此類植物在其樹幹上有蕨葉，但此蕨葉不會產生孢子。<ref name="Stewart">{{cite book|title=Paleobotany and the evolution of plants|url=https://archive.org/details/paleobotanyevolu0000stew|first1=Wilson A.|last2=Rothwell|first2=Gar W.|date=1993|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-0521382946|edition=2|last1=Stewart}}</ref>

[[煤系地層|煤系地層]]是生存於[[古生代|古生代]]時的植物的化石的主要來源。煤炭礦是採集化石最好的場所，而且[[碳|碳]]本身便是化石植物的殘留，雖然植物化石的結構細節很少會留在碳中。在[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]維多利亞公園中的化石森林裡，有發現[[鱗木屬|鱗木]]（''Lepidodendron''）的樹幹。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rBYwDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT119#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=Introducing Palaeontology: A Guide to Ancient Life|author=Patrick Wyse Jackson|edition=illustrated|publisher=Dunedin Academic Press|year=2010|isbn=9781903544426|page=119|access-date=2019-04-03|archive-date=2020-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408044219/https://books.google.com/books?id=rBYwDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT119#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

松柏和開花植物的根、莖及枝幹的化石可以在湖泊及海岸的[[中生代|中生代]]和[[新生代|新生代]]地層中被找到。[[加州紅木|加州紅木]]、[[木蘭屬|木蘭]]、[[櫟屬|櫟樹]]和[[棕櫚科|棕櫚樹]]等化石常被找到。<ref name="Stewart" />

[[石化木|石化木]]普遍存在於世界的部份地區，且最常在酸性及沙漠地區中所發現，因為那些地方很容易因[[侵蝕作用|侵蝕作用]]而暴露。石化木通常都被嚴重地矽化（有機質被[[二氧化矽|二氧化矽]]取代），且生殖組織常會被保存在良好的狀態。此類的樣本有些會使用寶石雕琢的裝置來切割及磨光。石化木的石化林已在每個大陸中被發現。<ref name="Stewart" />

[[舌羊齒屬|舌羊齒屬]]等種子蕨的化石廣泛分佈在[[南半球|南半球]]的數個大陸中，此一事實支持了[[阿爾弗雷德·魏格納|阿爾弗雷德·魏格納]]所提出的[[大陸漂移學說|大陸漂移學說]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Relation of Floras of the Southern Hemisphere to Continental Drift|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/1219279?origin=crossref|last=Schopf|first=James M.|date=1970-10|journal=Taxon|issue=5|doi=10.2307/1219279|volume=19|pages=657|access-date=2019-04-03|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403140613/https://www.jstor.org/stable/1219279?origin=crossref|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

目前无争议的最早的化石[[被子植物|被子植物]]是[[古果属|古果属]]植物<ref>Sun, G., Q. Ji, D.L. Dilcher, S. Zheng, K.C. Nixon & X. Wang 2002. [http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/296/5569/899?ck=nck&siteid=sci&ijkey=8dZ6zTqF606ps&keytype=ref Archaefructaceae, a New Basal Angiosperm Family] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/296/5569/899?ck=nck&siteid=sci&ijkey=8dZ6zTqF606ps&keytype=ref |date=20090217183754 }}. ''Science'' '''296'''(5569): 899–904.</ref><ref>Ji, Q., H. Li, L.M. Bowe, Y. Liu & D.W. Taylor 2004. {{cite web|url=http://faculty.frostburg.edu/biol/hli/research/Eoflora.pdf|title=Early Cretaceous ''Archaefructus eoflora'' sp. nov. with Bisexual Flowers from Beipiao, Western Liaoning, China.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929133513/http://faculty.frostburg.edu/biol/hli/research/Eoflora.pdf|archivedate=2007-09-29}} {{small|(3.11 MiB)}} ''Acta Geologica Sinica'' '''78'''(4): 883–896.</ref><ref name="NaturePlants2017">{{Cite journal|title=Palaeobotanical redux: revisiting the age of the angiosperms|journal=Nature Plants|doi=10.1038/nplants.2017.15|year=2017|volume=3|pages=Article number 17015|author3=Kaj Raunsgaard Pedersen|author4=Peter R. Crane|author1=Patrick S. Herendeen|author2=Else Marie Friis}}</ref>；最早的与现生类群亲近的化石被子植物是[[蒙特塞克藻|蒙特塞克藻]]，其与[[金鱼藻科|金鱼藻科]]互为[[姐妹群|姊妹类群]]<ref name="Bernard2015">{{Cite journal|title=Montsechia, an ancient aquatic angiosperm|url=http://www.pnas.org/lookup/doi/10.1073/pnas.1509241112|last=Gomez|first=Bernard|last2=Daviero-Gomez|first2=Véronique|date=2015-09-01|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=35|doi=10.1073/pnas.1509241112|volume=112|pages=10985–10988|pmc=4568254|pmid=26283347|last3=Coiffard|first3=Clément|last4=Martín-Closas|first4=Carles|last5=Dilcher|first5=David L.|access-date=2019-04-03|archive-date=2019-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701103349/https://www.pnas.org/content/112/35/10985|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另有[[潘氏真花|潘氏真花]]等位置未定的古种子植物，部分学者主张其为被子植物<ref name="Liu2015">{{Cite journal|title=A perfect flower from the Jurassic of China|url=https://www.tandfonline.com/action/captchaChallenge?redirectUri=%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F08912963.2015.1020423|last=Liu|first=Zhong-Jian|last2=Wang|first2=Xin|date=2015-03-16|journal=Historical Biology|issue=5|doi=10.1080/08912963.2015.1020423|volume=28|pages=707–719|language=en|issn=0891-2963|pmc=4841032|pmid=27134345|access-date=2019-03-10|archive-date=2021-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211122230725/https://www.tandfonline.com/action/captchaChallenge?redirectUri=%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F08912963.2015.1020423|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也有学者质疑其为[[松柏門|松柏类]]裸子植物<ref name="NaturePlants2017" />。若干项关于被子植物起源时间的研究认为，依据[[分子鐘|分子钟]]的结论，被子植物可能起源于[[侏罗纪|侏罗纪]]甚至[[三叠纪|三叠纪]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Establishing a time-scale for plant evolution|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1111/j.1469-8137.2011.03794.x|last=Clarke|first=John T.|last2=Warnock|first2=Rachel C. M.|date=2011-10|journal=New Phytologist|issue=1|doi=10.1111/j.1469-8137.2011.03794.x|volume=192|pages=266–301|language=en|last3=Donoghue|first3=Philip C. J.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The timescale of early land plant evolution|url=http://www.pnas.org/lookup/doi/10.1073/pnas.1719588115|last=Morris|first=Jennifer L.|last2=Puttick|first2=Mark N.|date=2018-03-06|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=10|doi=10.1073/pnas.1719588115|volume=115|pages=E2274–E2283|language=en|issn=0027-8424|pmc=PMC5877938|pmid=29463716|last3=Clark|first3=James W.|last4=Edwards|first4=Dianne|last5=Kenrick|first5=Paul|last6=Pressel|first6=Silvia|last7=Wellman|first7=Charles H.|last8=Yang|first8=Ziheng|last9=Schneider|first9=Harald}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Past Sure is Tense: On Interpreting Phylogenetic Divergence Time Estimates|url=https://academic.oup.com/sysbio/article/67/2/340/4107448|last=Brown|first=Joseph W|last2=Smith|first2=Stephen A|date=2018-03-01|journal=Systematic Biology|issue=2|doi=10.1093/sysbio/syx074|volume=67|pages=340–353|language=en|issn=1063-5157|access-date=2019-04-11|archive-date=2019-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411064527/https://academic.oup.com/sysbio/article/67/2/340/4107448|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但尚无可靠的化石证据支持<ref name="NaturePlants2017" />，分析指出，这可能是由于早期被子植物在生态上并不重要，或者其生活在[[石化|化石化作用]]难以发生的环境中<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Constraining uncertainty in the timescale of angiosperm evolution and the veracity of a Cretaceous Terrestrial Revolution|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1111/nph.15011|last=Barba-Montoya|first=Jose|last2=dos Reis|first2=Mario|date=2018-04|journal=New Phytologist|issue=2|doi=10.1111/nph.15011|volume=218|pages=819–834|language=en|pmc=PMC6055841|pmid=29399804|last3=Schneider|first3=Harald|last4=Donoghue|first4=Philip C. J.|last5=Yang|first5=Ziheng}}</ref>。

